-## Network Ports (multi-client setup)
-
-| Client | HTTP RPC | WS RPC | P2P | Discovery |
-|--------|----------|--------|-----|-----------|
-| core-geth | 8545 | 8546 | 30303 | 30303 |
-| besu | 8548 | 8549 | 30304 | 30304 |
-| fukuii | 8553 | 8552 | 30305 | 30305 |
